human_system_low,electrical hum,733737,60Hz electrical mains hum,"60, 60Hz, america, backrooms, buzz, canada, cycle, electric, electrical, electricity, fridge, hum, mains, noise, north, power, refrigerator, transformer","60Hz mains hum (60-cycle hum) heard in electrical appliances in North America. Commonly heard from fridges, transformers, and of course, fluorescent lights. 

Also commonly associated with the Backrooms.",http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/,wav,5.45454,chungus43A,412,4.9411764705882355,2024-04-28T01:53:41Z,1047316,0,16,48000.0,2,https://cdn.freesound.org/previews/733/733737_12024110-hq.mp3,https://cdn.freesound.org/previews/733/733737_12024110-lq.mp3,https://cdn.freesound.org/displays/733/733737_12024110_spec_M.jpg,https://cdn.freesound.org/displays/733/733737_12024110_wave_M.png,https://freesound.org/people/chungus43A/sounds/733737/,1,112.0,,193.208,10.415,0.025,0.11,49.886,5.337,,True
human_system_low,electrical hum,721813,BPSN electrical hum 2,"300hz, 81-71, 81-717, apu, bpsn, budapest, electric, electrical, hep, hum, inverter, locomotive, metro, moscow, noise, novosibirsk, prague, saint-petersburg, static, subway, train, transformer","This sound was synthesized in <a href=""http://beepbox.co"" rel=""nofollow"">beepbox.co</a>

This is the sound of the BPSN static inverter hum heard on the 81-717 subway trains found around the world, most commonly heard in Saint Petersburg, Moscow, Prague, and Budapest's metro systems. This is a 300 hertz electrical hum produced by a transformer that converts 750 volts from the contact rail to 220V 50Hz AC for the interior lights and 80V DC for the control circuits. Similar static inverters are used to provide head-end power (HEP) for locomotives around the world.",http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/,wav,12.8,chungus43A,184,5.0,2024-02-05T02:59:02Z,2457644,0,16,48000.0,2,https://cdn.freesound.org/previews/721/721813_12024110-hq.mp3,https://cdn.freesound.org/previews/721/721813_12024110-lq.mp3,https://cdn.freesound.org/displays/721/721813_12024110_spec_M.jpg,https://cdn.freesound.org/displays/721/721813_12024110_wave_M.png,https://freesound.org/people/chungus43A/sounds/721813/,2,81.0,,945.871,5.541,1.0,0.005,44.097,12.542,,True
