human_system_low,transformer hum,262510,Gym Lights Powering Up,"ball, basketball, buzz, capacitor, circuitry, circuits, click, energize, generator, gym, gymnasium, hum, indoor, indoors, juice, lights, overhead, power, power-up, switch, thrum, transformer, volleyball, warm-up","This is a (mediocre) recording of gym lights being powered on. There is the distinct hum of the transformer/capacitor or whatever helps power them running in the background and then a distinctive click and electronic thud as the lights come on followed by the buzz of the overhead lights as they are warming up. 

