human_system_low,transformer hum,567723,BORIERO_Nolwen_2020_2021_Monster breathing.wav,"Monster, breathing, creature, dinosaur, dragon, fx, monster, noise, sf","I recorded my cat's purr, and transformed it into the breath of a monster or fantastic creature.. I followed these steps : 

1.	Importing my cat's purrs
2.	Change speed: speed multiplier: 0.610, change percentage: -39,000
3.	Change the height: from 43.109 to 30.176
4.	Delete parts of the audio to avoid the ""hum"" effect
5.	Generate a silence: 1sc
6.	Fade in and out certain parts of the audio
7.	Copy and paste parts of the audio in order to have a more efficient opening fade in the 2nd part of the audio",http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/,wav,9.81848,iut_Paris8,2165,4.714285714285714,2021-04-12T16:57:32Z,1299030,0,24,44100.0,1,https://cdn.freesound.org/previews/567/567723_907124-hq.mp3,https://cdn.freesound.org/previews/567/567723_907124-lq.mp3,https://cdn.freesound.org/displays/567/567723_907124_spec_M.jpg,https://cdn.freesound.org/displays/567/567723_907124_wave_M.png,https://freesound.org/people/iut_Paris8/sounds/567723/,76,130.0,,1289.698,1.837,1.0,0.004,44.216,6.877,,True
human_system_low,transformer hum,726228,WRESTLING ROBOT,"film, robotics, wrestling","📺 Immerse Yourself in the World of Television with These Captivating Sounds! 📺

